org.cxio.core.interfaces

Interface AspectFragmentReader

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractFragmentReader, AnonymousFragmentReader, CartesianLayoutFragmentReader, CyGroupsFragmentReader, CyViewsFragmentReader, CyVisualPropertiesFragmentReader, EdgeAttributesFragmentReader, EdgesFragmentReader, HiddenAttributesFragmentReader, NetworkAttributesFragmentReader, NetworkRelationsFragmentReader, NodeAttributesFragmentReader, NodesFragmentReader, SubNetworkFragmentReader

    public interface AspectFragmentReader
    The interface for Aspect Fragment readers (Aspect Fragments are lists of Aspect Elements). Each AspectElement implementation needs to have a corresponding AspectFragmentReader.
    Author:
    cmzmasek

      • readAspectFragment

        java.util.List<AspectElement> readAspectFragment(com.fasterxml.jackson.core.JsonParser jp)
                                          throws java.io.IOException
        This is the main method of AspectFragmentReaders. It takes a JsonParser from Jackson Faster XML library http://fasterxml.github.io/jackson-core/javadoc /2.0.0/com/fasterxml/jackson/core/JsonParser.html and returns a list of AspectElements (a aspect fragment).
        Parameters:
